init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are a young man living in a small village in the north of England at the end of the nineteenth century.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You notice a sparrow fall down from the sky to the ground.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You bend down to pick up the bird, and it flies away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ride the bus to Leeds.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The person behind the counter looks at you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You then walk out of the chemist's shop.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You take the bottle of codeine and lift it up to your mouth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You walk out of the subway and into a shopping centre.
